dcterms:description: The ISIC 2018 dataset consists of high-resolution, RGB images of seven classes of skin lesions. For the experiments, only two classes (melanoma and dermatofibroma) are used, with a focus on addressing class imbalance in the dataset.
dcterms:title: ISIC 2018
